{"tid":1890975,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警告，銀離子水不殺病毒","createTime":"2020-02-21T13:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T15:31:45.000Z","uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b08f029aed1e45aaa16b1cd2a2e51c8e2f912c08","tid":1890975,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"的確，除了這間店鋪，在網上亦有不少影片，宣揚銀離子水的功效。但是，化學博士K.Kwong則表示，銀離子水絕對不能替代酒精。「銀離子不可以消滅病毒的，但可以消滅細菌，大部分細菌都可以，因為銀本身是可以殺菌的。」眾所周知，武漢肺炎是一種冠狀病毒，單單殺菌，絕對不能應對疫情：「殺菌消毒要全部做到，我們才可以稱為殺菌消毒劑，英文就是antiseptic，即可以全部做到。我們平日用的漂白水，就可以全部做到，酒精亦可以全部做到。」"},{"pid":"73d77b05b188e7f5031601317f56630fe625e546","tid":1890975,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48886c855c09db90d0ab186db779de5352ea89ee","tid":1890975,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9273e33d45d0a3f5e1d874c54dc473b5b1721ae","tid":1890975,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}